Package: CovarBalDiagEval
Type: Package
Title: Evaluating the fitness of various statistics to measure covariate balance.
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Joshua Ide [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Joshua Ide <jdi212@lehigh.edu>
Description: A framework for evaluating the use of different statistics (starting with standardized mean difference [SMD]) to measure covariate balance.
